'''馬克·加尼爾'''（{{lang-en|Mark Garnier}}，{{bd|1963年|2月26日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]政治人物<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=59418 |date=13 May 2010 |startpage=8746}}</ref>，他的黨籍是[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]。自2010年開始，他擔任[[懷爾森林_(英國國會選區)|懷爾森林]]選區選出的英國下議院議員<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theyworkforyou.com/mp/mark_garnier/wyre_forest |title=TheyWorkForYou.com |access-date=2016-03-06 |archive-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601164756/http://www.theyworkforyou.com/mp/mark_garnier/wyre_forest |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/election2010/results/constituency/f34.stm |title=BBC Election 2010 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |archive-date=2017-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828201330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/election2010/results/constituency/f34.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他出生在倫敦。

2017年，加尼爾由於让其秘书帮他的妻子与情妇购买情趣用品，遭[[英国内阁办公厅|英国内阁办公厅]]调查。<ref name="Wootson">{{cite news|last1=Wootson Jr|first1=Cleve R.|title=A British minister admits he made his secretary buy sex toys as #MeToo hits Parliament|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/10/29/a-british-minister-admits-he-made-his-secretary-buy-sex-toys-as-metoo-hits-parliament/|accessdate=2017-10-29|work=The Washington Post|date=2017-10-29|archive-date=2017-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171103143655/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/10/29/a-british-minister-admits-he-made-his-secretary-buy-sex-toys-as-metoo-hits-parliament/|dead-url=no}}</ref>调查结果称加尔尼并未触犯法律且事情发生于就任大臣之前。

